       "label": "AU-10(01)(a)",
       "prose": {
        "en": "the identity of the information producer is bound with the information to {param:au-10.01_odp};"
       }
      },
      {
       "id": "au-10.1_obj.b",
       "label": "AU-10(01)(b)",
       "prose": {
        "en": "the means for authorized individuals to determine the identity of the producer of the information is provided."
       }
